metadata.name: Never Give Up #1/100
metadata.description:
This was painted years ago and had since faded, but days before I took this photo, I saw it was repainted. I thought it might look good at sunrise. I never imagined capturing the sun coming through the beach fence like this. Never give up. 

Photo taken Jan. 28, 2023 in Ventnor City, New Jersey by Shaun R. Smith.
